	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=39551><span id=Guru>Osano</span></a><br><b><span id=Guru>Guru</span></b><br><span id=notbold>171 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.34]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Azure sleeves are quite simply the best sleeve item you can own that's not planar or better.&nbsp;&nbsp;Other than gatorscale, you might look for Drake Hide, which is the SolA Bartender's rare drop.  These will only run you about 100PP.  The tailored Wu's Sleeves are probably your best alternative though.<br><br>Interesting price/availability variance between certain servers too, depending on which areas get hunted more.  Azure sleeves on T-P are only 500-700P while I've noticed that prices on other items Keyeluke has quoted are a good bit below what they are on T-P</p>&nbsp;<br>Osano<br>Level 44 Human Monk<br>Tholuxe-Paells</td></td></tr>
